# Walkthrough: Cleanup and Fixes for Flutter Partner App

## Overview
This walkthrough details the changes made to remove mock data, ensure data persistence, and fix CRUD operations in the Flutter Partner App.

## Changes Made

### 1. Removal of Mock Data
- **Deleted Mock Services**: Removed [lib/services/auth_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/auth_service.dart), [lib/services/payment_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/payment_service.dart), and [lib/services/connectivity_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/connectivity_service.dart).
- **Refactored AppState**: Updated [lib/providers/app_state.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/providers/app_state.dart) to remove dependencies on mock services and enforce usage of real API repositories ([AuthRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/auth_repository.dart#7-298), [CustomerRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/customer_repository.dart#5-210), [WalletRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/wallet_repository.dart#5-190), [PlanRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/plan_repository.dart#5-137), [RouterRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/router_repository.dart#5-152)).
- **Removed Feature Flags**: Removed `ApiConfig.useRemoteApi` usage, as the app now exclusively uses the real API.

### 2. Data Persistence
- **Verified TokenStorage**: Confirmed [lib/services/api/token_storage.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/api/token_storage.dart) correctly uses `FlutterSecureStorage` (mobile/desktop) and `SharedPreferences` (web) to persist JWT tokens.
- **App Initialization**: Verified [lib/main.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/main.dart) and [lib/feature/launch/splash_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/feature/launch/splash_screen.dart) correctly call `AppState.checkAuthStatus()` on startup to rehydrate the user session from stored tokens.

### 3. CRUD Operation Fixes
- **Pagination Fixes**:
    - Updated `AppState.loadUsers()` to use `CustomerRepository.fetchAllCustomers()` instead of paginated [fetchCustomers()](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/customer_repository.dart#10-49). This ensures newly created users (who might be on later pages) are visible in the list.
    - Updated `AppState.loadTransactions()` to use `WalletRepository.fetchAllTransactions()` to ensure all transactions are loaded.
- **Consistency Updates**:
    - Consolidated plan-related operations in [AppState](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/providers/app_state.dart#34-774) to use [PlanRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/plan_repository.dart#5-137) exclusively (previously mixed with [WalletRepository](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/wallet_repository.dart#5-190)).
- **List Refreshing**:
    - Updated [createUser](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/auth_service.dart#102-115), [updateUser](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/auth_service.dart#116-129), [deleteUser](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/auth_service.dart#130-133), [createPlan](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/repositories/plan_repository.dart#35-52), [createRouter](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/services/connectivity_service.dart#11-25) in [AppState](file:///c:/Users/ELITEX21012G2/antigravity_partnerapp/Flutter_partnerapp/lib/providers/app_state.dart#34-774) to explicitly reload the relevant data lists after a successful operation, ensuring the UI reflects changes immediately.

